OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FWatch ITV News Central Health
OL,7,FCorrespondent Hannah Bechelet's report
OL,9,FOn the Frailty Ward in Russell's Hall
OL,10,FHospital the Matron told me the NHS
OL,11,Fisn't broken, and that innovations
OL,12,Flike the Virtual Ward system they have
OL,13,Fbeen using for the past two-and-a-half
OL,14,Fyears prove it.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/16
