OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FOver the next couple of hours I was
OL,7,Fable to see for myself how the Virtual
OL,8,FWard works, observing a multi-
OL,9,Fdisciplinary meeting about 93-year-old
OL,10,FDoreen Whittingham and then meeting
OL,11,Fher myself. She told me clearly how
OL,12,Fgrateful she was to be treated at home
OL,13,Fand how little she felt she would have
OL,14,Fbeen able to do if she'd be 'stuck in
OL,15,Fhospital.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
