OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FIt therefore wasn't hard to see the
OL,7,Fbenefits of a scheme that has a simple
OL,8,Fpremise - where people can have their
OL,9,Fsymptoms managed effectively at home,
OL,10,Fkeep them there instead of bringing
OL,11,Fthem into hospital, where they are
OL,12,Finevitably rather stationary and can
OL,13,Frapidly become reconditioned.
OL,15,FSince the Dudley hospital started
OL,16,Fhosting 'virtual wards' in January
OL,17,F2023, 1,800 people have been on one,
OL,18,Fsaving almost 10,000 bed days, which
OL,19,Ffrees up space for those who cannot be
OL,20,Ftreated at home.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
