OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FThe wards supported the Matron's
OL,7,Fargument for innovation being the
OL,8,Ffuture of the NHS, and I have seen a
OL,9,Flot of these different innovations
OL,10,Fover the last couple of months as I
OL,11,Fhave been given access to different
OL,12,Fparts of the NHS that we don't always
OL,13,Fsee, and aren't always aware of.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
