OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FWith the NHS's new 10-year plan having
OL,7,Fa big focus on preventative care, my
OL,8,Ffirst stop was spending the morning
OL,9,Fwith a team from Worcestershire who
OL,10,Ftake vans out into the community to
OL,11,Fget to people who cannot, or might
OL,12,Fnot, have access to a GPs. They give
OL,13,Fpeople free health checks, and sign
OL,14,Fthem up with a GP where necessary.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
