OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FA local GP manager there told me that
OL,7,Fshe is constantly surprised how many
OL,8,Fpeople aren't registered with a GP,
OL,9,Fbut said that without being signed up
OL,10,Fpeople are missing vital screenings
OL,11,Fthat could save their lives. In fact,
OL,12,Fnot being registered with a GP surgery
OL,13,Fis one of the biggest drivers of
OL,14,Fhealth inequality.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
