OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FWhilst standing outside the van I saw
OL,7,Fa woman who didn't look well be
OL,8,Fencouraged to speak to the nurses. She
OL,9,Fhad only popped by to use the
OL,10,Fcommunity cafe, but by seeing the
OL,11,Fteam, was immediately found a GP
OL,12,Fappointment as they had concerns about
OL,13,Fher. That's a GP appointment she
OL,14,Fwouldn't have had without the van
OL,15,Fbeing there.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
