OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FWe often hear of problems getting
OL,7,Fappointments as GPs are busy, but many
OL,8,Ftake for granted that they have a
OL,9,Flocal GP and they know where to go if
OL,10,Fthey are ill. The vans are helping
OL,11,Fmake sure everyone has that same
OL,12,Faccess. It's a simple idea, but one
OL,13,Fthat has helped more than 4,500 in two
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FPrevention is at the heart of another
OL,17,Finitiative I saw over in East
OL,18,FBirmingham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
