OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FA first of its kind, called a Locality
OL,7,FHub, based in Washwood Heath, brings
OL,8,Fhospital specialists, community teams,
OL,9,FGPs, social care and mental health
OL,10,Fservices together to respond to the
OL,11,Flocal need.
OL,13,FIn that part of Birmingham it
OL,14,Fspecially targets help at those with
OL,15,Fheart conditions and in need of
OL,16,Frespiratory care. And it's having a
OL,17,F30% reduction in hospital admissions
OL,18,Ffor those it is helping.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
