OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FThe stories I heard were literally
OL,7,Flife-changing - of people who were
OL,8,Fregularly calling an ambulance but now
OL,9,Fhave their condition managed locally
OL,10,Fand have no need to call an ambulance
OL,11,Fat all.
OL,13,FI also spent time in their control
OL,14,Fcentre where they rely heavily on data
OL,15,Fto see who needs help. The team can
OL,16,Fsee everyone who called an ambulance
OL,17,Fin East Birmingham the day before and
OL,18,Fwhy, and everyone who didn't get taken
OL,19,Fto hospital gets a follow up call.
OL,20,FThose in hospital are assessed to see
OL,21,Fif care could be based at home.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
