OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FEchoing the thoughts of the Matron in
OL,7,FDudley about the NHS being broken, the
OL,8,FChief Executive of the Trust that runs
OL,9,Fthe Hub told me that the idea had been
OL,10,F'born out of some of the very real
OL,11,Fpressure, the health and social care
OL,12,Fsystem face,' but he went on to say
OL,13,Fhow 'this attempt to get upstream and
OL,14,Fbe more preventative is what this is
OL,15,Fall about.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
