OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FAnd over in Sandwell, I saw a
OL,7,Fdifferent kind of preventative
OL,8,Fhealthcare- collaborative working
OL,9,Fbetween the local NHS Trust and the
OL,10,FCouncil to make sure that people going
OL,11,Fhome from hospital aren't readmitted.
OL,13,FWith that aim, a purpose built
OL,14,Ffacility opened in November 2022,
OL,15,Faimed at helping people prepare to go
OL,16,Fhome when they've been in hospital for
OL,17,Fa long time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
