OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FSpending the afternoon there, I met
OL,7,Ftwo women who said their stay in
OL,8,FHarvest View had given them the
OL,9,Fstrength, both physically and
OL,10,Fmentally, to go home after a long stay
OL,11,Fin hospital. Jasbir had suffered a bad
OL,12,Finjury to her leg and needed help
OL,13,Fregaining everyday skills such as
OL,14,Fclimbing stairs and stacking the
OL,15,Fdishwasher before she went home.
OL,16,FMargaret was severely underweight but
OL,17,Ffound her time being cared for in
OL,18,FRowley Regis, alongside other friendly
OL,19,Ffaces, meant she had put weight on and
OL,20,Fwas more confident about living alone
OL,21,Fagain.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
