OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FLike many of the other initiatives I
OL,7,Fsaw, Harvest View had a simple premise
OL,8,F- help people gain back the
OL,9,Findependence they lost in hospital.
OL,10,FAnd it's keeping people out of care
OL,11,Fhomes, and avoiding re-admitance to
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/16
