OL,3,CIs innovation the fix for the 'broken'
OL,4,CNHS?
OL,6,FWith all these initiatives in mind, I
OL,7,Fcome back to the chat I had with the
OL,8,FMatron in Dudley. There is a lot of
OL,9,Ftalk about the NHS being broken, and I
OL,10,Fam sure that discussions about funding
OL,11,Fwill continue. But what I have seen
OL,12,Fare clear, bold ways of thinking and
OL,13,Fworking that are helping people at all
OL,14,Fstages of their health journey. If the
OL,15,FNHS is to have a healthy future,
OL,16,Finnovation is key.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/16
